g.text: 1.2: request data( snsNum ) to verify vaccine schedule
6: confirms that the data is correct
5.2: shows the typed data and requests a confirmation
6.3: informs that the SNS user doesn't have vaccination schedule for that day and time
4.4: informs that the SNS user has a vaccination schedule for that day and time
1: starts registering the arrival of the SNS user
